### [List of United Arab Emirates women Twenty20 International cricketers](/List_of_United_Arab_Emirates_women_Twenty20_International_cricketers)

This is a chronicle of the women who have represented the [United Arab Emirates](/United_Arab_Emirates) in the sport of [cricket](/cricket) in the [Twenty20 International](/Twenty20_International) format. It’s a roster, a tally, a testament to those who’ve stepped onto the pitch under the UAE banner in this electrifying, quick-fire version of the game. You want a list? Fine. But understand, these aren’t just names on a page. They are individuals who’ve faced the pressure, the roar of the crowd, the sting of defeat, and the fleeting triumph that defines [Twenty20 cricket](/Twenty20_cricket).

The path to representing a nation in international [cricket](/cricket) is rarely paved with ease. For these women, it signifies years of dedication, relentless practice, and a singular passion for the sport. The [United Arab Emirates](/United_Arab_Emirates), a nation with a burgeoning [cricket](/cricket) culture, has seen its women’s team participate in numerous [Twenty20 International](/Twenty20_International) fixtures, a format known for its explosive batting, strategic bowling, and often unpredictable outcomes. This list serves as a permanent record, a digital monument to their contributions.

#### Background

The journey of women’s [cricket](/cricket) in the [United Arab Emirates](/United_Arab_Emirates) mirrors the nation’s own rapid development. While [cricket](/cricket) has deep roots in the region, primarily through its expatriate population, the formalization and promotion of the women’s game have seen significant strides in recent decades. The establishment of a dedicated women’s national team and their subsequent participation in international competitions, including the [Twenty20 International](/Twenty20_International) arena, is a crucial step in this evolution.

The [International Cricket Council (ICC)](/International_Cricket_Council) plays a pivotal role in sanctioning [Twenty20 International](/Twenty20_International) matches, a format that has gained immense popularity worldwide due to its fast pace and entertainment value. For Associate and Affiliate members like the [United Arab Emirates](/United_Arab_Emirates), the [T20I](/T20_International) format offers a more accessible pathway to international competition compared to the longer formats of [Test cricket](/Test_cricket) and [One Day Internationals](/One_Day_International). This allows emerging nations to test their mettle against established teams and gain invaluable experience on the global stage.

The players listed here have earned their caps through performance, perseverance, and a commitment to the sport. Each name represents a story of ambition, sacrifice, and the pursuit of excellence in a demanding global sport. They are pioneers, carving out a space for women in [cricket](/cricket) within the UAE and inspiring future generations.

